snippet.title: DarkSwarm - Sneak Peek Trailer
snippet.description:
DarkSwarm is a 1-4 player co-op, top-down action game, featuring procedural generation and class based progression. 

WISHLIST NOW ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2303200/DarkSwarm/

This Sneak Peek trailer showcases the latest development from the Bitfire Games team as of October 2023. 

DarkSwarm is expected to release into Steam Early Access in 2025

Developer
Bitfire Games

Publisher
Ghost Ship Publishing

Find out more:
http://darkswarm.io/
https://www.ghostship.dk/publishing/
